                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክርስቲያን</foreign>
               </form>
               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp> <lbl expand="pluralis">Pl.</lbl> (Sing. non usitatur) <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> Christiani </quote></cit> <ref cRef="Act." loc="11,26">Act. 11,26</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኮኑ፡ አበዊሁ፡ ክርስቲያነ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sx. Nah." loc="5.">Sx. Nah. 5.</ref> – De <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንኡስ፡</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዐቢይ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</foreign> vid. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንኡስ፡</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዐቢይ፡</foreign> – Tritissima est vox composita <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> (domus Christianorum) </quote></cit>, <lbl expand="pluralis">Pl.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያናት፡</foreign> (ut <ref cRef="Act." loc="8,1">Act. 8,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Act." loc="16,5">Act. 16,5</ref> <lbl expand="romanae editionis">rom.</lbl>), at plerumque <foreign xml:lang="gez">አብያተ፡ ክርስቲያናት፡</foreign>, <gramGrp> <gen value="not found">m.</gen> </gramGrp> et <gramGrp> <gen value="femininus">fem.</gen> </gramGrp>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> ecclesia </quote></cit> <sense n="a" xml:id="Da"> aedes, ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ትኩን፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ኑኃ፡ መንገለ፡ ምሥራቅ፡ ወክልኤ፡ ሕዋራት፡ ውስተ፡ ገበዋቲሃ፡ በአምሳለ፡ ሐመር፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Did." loc="12.">Did. 12.</ref> </sense> <sense n="b" xml:id="Db"> coetus fidelium: <ref cRef="Asc. Jes." loc="3,16">Asc. Jes. 3,16</ref>; <ref cRef="Apoc." loc="1,4">Apoc. 1,4</ref>; <ref cRef="Apoc." loc="1,11">Apoc. 1,11</ref>; <ref cRef="Apoc." loc="2,1">Apoc. 2,1</ref> <lbl expand="sequens">seq.</lbl>; <ref cRef="Act." loc="8,3">Act. 8,3</ref>; <ref cRef="Matth." loc="16,18">Matth. 16,18</ref>; <ref cRef="Matth." loc="18,17">Matth. 18,17</ref>; <ref cRef="Did." loc="3">Did. 3</ref>; <ref cRef="Did." loc="4">Did. 4</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">አብያተ፡ ክርስቲያናት፡ በመዋዕሊሁ፡ ርቱዓን፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sx. Mag." loc="24">Sx. Mag. 24</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ይዕቀብ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያኖ፡</foreign> (sic) <ref cRef="Sx. Mag." loc="2">Sx. Mag. 2</ref>; al.</sense> </sense>
               
            <sense xml:id="Tmain" xml:lang="en" source="#traces"> <ptr target="#D1"/><sense n="a" xml:id="Ta"> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዓቢየ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote> ʾābiyya krǝstiyān </quote></cit> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወበምህሮ፡ ቃለ፡ ሃይማኖትሰ፡ ለምዕመናን፡ ዓቢየ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወለንኡሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</foreign> ‘<cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><quote> But regarding the teaching of the word of faith to the faithful — (that is,) the great Christians — and the catechumens </quote></cit>’ <bibl><ptr target="bm:Getatchew2013MeshafeBerhanT"/><citedRange unit="page"> 12 (ed.)</citedRange></bibl>, <bibl><ptr target="bm:Getatchew2013MeshafeBerhanV"/><citedRange unit="page"> 9 (tr.)</citedRange></bibl> (‘The term <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote> ʾabiyyä krǝstiyan </quote></cit>, coined obviously to constrast the committed faithful “who are in the convenant,” with the catechumens, called <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote> nǝʾusä krǝstiyan </quote></cit>.’ <bibl><ptr target="bm:Getatchew2013MeshafeBerhanV"/><citedRange unit="page"> 9 n. 36</citedRange></bibl>), <lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዐቢይ፡</foreign> </sense> <sense n="b" xml:id="Tb"> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንኡሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote> nǝʾusa krǝstiyān </quote></cit> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወዘይቤሂ፡ ኡሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ይትገኃሡ፡ ከመ፡ ይቁሙ፡ ኡሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ እንተ፡ ባሕቲቶሙ፡ ወጺኦሙ፡ አፍአ።</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><quote> And the reason he said, “Let catechumens be removed”, is so that the catechumens may go out, to stand outside by themselves </quote></cit> <bibl><ptr target="bm:Getatchew2013MeshafeBerhanT"/><citedRange unit="page"> 8 (ed.)</citedRange></bibl>, <bibl><ptr target="bm:Getatchew2013MeshafeBerhanV"/><citedRange unit="page"> 6 (tr.)</citedRange></bibl>, <lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንኡስ፡</foreign> </sense></sense>
